  "heading_latex": "\\textrm{Axiom of Extension}",
  "body_text": null,
  "page": null,
  "source": "[\\axiom.of.extension]\nAxiom: \"Axiom of Extension\"\ngiven: A, B is \\set\nthen: A = B\niff:\n. forAll: x is \\set\n  then:\n  . have: x \"in\" A\n    iff: x \"in\" B\nDocumented:\n. description: \"Two sets are equal if and only if they contain precisely the same elements, so the only thing which matters about a set is which elements it has.\"\nId: \"7b04025f-2483-4935-8ed4-11d22b87b354\"",
